values.description:
Stadimax is a newly formed partnership that uniquely combines feasibility, capital, development, revenue generation and management services specific to stadia and arena development, into an integrated offering.

The team's past experience includes, but is not limited to:

- Wembley Stadium, London, UK;
- Etihad Stadium, Melbourne, Australia;
- American Express Community Stadium, Brighton, UK;
- Reebok Stadium, Bolton, UK;
- Ricoh Arena, Coventry, UK;
- KC Stadium, Hull, UK;
- John Smith Stadium, Huddersfield, UK.

We offer a wide range of services to enable development of sports venues in the UK, Australia and elsewhere globally, with the aim of offering high value services that will ensure commercially successful stadia and arenas.  We work on both new build and refurbishments.
